{"tid":2036111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁天琦於「捍衛民主・重奪主權」集會演講","createTime":"2020-05-26T09:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T10:07:26.000Z","uid":104845,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"359162a1f1285968df0a5293373bd4372a802db4","tid":2036111,"uid":104845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:22:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkindigenous/videos/1756609607926277/UzpfSTE1NDY5MjU0ODIyMjgwMjU6Vks6MTc1NjYwOTYwNzkyNjI3Nw/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkindigenous%2Fvideos%2F1756609607926277%2FUzpfSTE1NDY5MjU0ODIyMjgwMjU6Vks6MTc1NjYwOTYwNzkyNjI3Nw%2F&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMA0PYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=3b50d2d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkindigenous/videos/1756609607926277/UzpfSTE1NDY5MjU0ODIyMjgwMjU6Vks6MTc1NjYwOTYwNzkyNjI3Nw/</a><br />\n二零一六年八月五日，梁天琦與其他被選舉管理委員會禁止參選的參選人於香港民族黨的「捍衛民主・重奪主權」集會中演說，發表長達二十分鐘的發言。<br />\n<br />\n梁天琦發言共分成四部份：<span style=\"color: red;\">政治、政府、革命、夢想</span>。<br />\n<br />\n政治(00:00-04:12)<br />\n政治是權力的分配，香港的主權不在北京或香港政府，而在<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人民</span>。<br />\n而革命是要奪回在獨裁的社會中，人民應有的權利。<br />\n<br />\n政府(04:13-06:13)<br />\n政府擁有武力、權力，政府所說的法律就是法律，政府的本質就是一個暴力的機構。<br />\n面對無賴的政府不須再講仁義道德，<span style=\"color: red;\">即使成為無賴亦要用盡必要的方法去推翻政府</span>。<br />\n<br />\n革命(06:14-11:37)<br />\n革命是社會權力分配根本性的改變，人民不再要求政府改革，而是下而上地扭轉社會的權力結構。<br />\n要追隨理念而非追隨個人，要成為社會上的主流，終有一日會成功。<br />\n<br />\n夢想(11:38-16:15)<br />\n講述梁天琦個人追求夢想之路，一年前後的反差，勸勉眾人追逐夢想。<br />\n即使當下看似黑暗，但黎明一定會到來。<br />\n<br />\n527來臨之際，當打氣又好，回血又好，都想有更多的人睇下條片。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n民族自強，香港獨立。<br />\n街頭見。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V9MNrJv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV9MNrJv.png&h=8ecb1bf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/afNAABR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FafNAABR.jpg&h=b2f1ce61&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"175d3782d3e2a804f67c089b40b990d269f74a68","tid":2036111,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:24:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22f9da9aa90cb1f16dd8eca7d9535ad0a791bc8e","tid":2036111,"uid":104845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:25:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16e749cbbd00b9720c479d431c61a2a71c2a4e9f","tid":2036111,"uid":104845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:27:27.000Z","msg":"可能好多人都睇過 推"},{"pid":"ce89c13d4b531b8bd8b3a646bf21cff3ec711fbe","tid":2036111,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:28:03.000Z","msg":"[預言] 100%準確527朝早邊度最多人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2036097\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2036097</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a0e27a8d6faab3f306169c2e51f1a4ad237b3b68","tid":2036111,"uid":104845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:30:22.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"57d2c0ac400d39d5f45a36ec4afd3ca57a44c2bd","tid":2036111,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adbeeb10717898280248124e27642bc590349310","tid":2036111,"uid":104845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:31:55.000Z","msg":"一推再推"},{"pid":"377c5d2f0ba224507c88ce037ce04b2b9d0e2193","tid":2036111,"uid":104845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:32:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d3d871c8526eaec01ad848cc9eb8ba3dc4c7e9f","tid":2036111,"uid":41512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:36:58.000Z","msg